reviews.review_text:
Best AUD of this date So
I listen to the other versions of this show
all the rest have either too much echo (Andrew F)
or too much audience noise, and sound like they're miles away.


Thus, this is the best aud of this date IMO.

4.3 for show
+ for aud, so other fans can find this amongst the choices
